# User stories

### №1

As a user I can book excursions for fun (interesting to know about the city, visit the historical and beautiful places, etc.)

### №2

As a user, I can view reviews from other users to create their idea of ​​the excursions / place.

###No. 3

As a user I can post reviews for expression and the creation of a certain image of the tour / company.

### №4

As a user I can take pictures and post a description and location on the map of places that I find memorable / beautiful / interesting to visit and put them in your profile to attract public attention to me and an increase in the number of subscribers.

### №5

As a user I can leave not only feedback, but also comments on the sites, laid out by other users.

### №6

As an advertiser, I can place their targeted advertising on users.

### №7

As a guest I can view photos and descriptions of other users.

### №8

As a guest I can register.

### №9

As a guest I can log on to a previously created an account.

### №10

As a user I can delete my account.

### №11

As a user I can change the login credentials.

### №12

As a user I can do some of the fields account visible / not visible to other users.

### №13

As a user I can appreciate the route / tour / photo and description of the location.

### №14

As an administrator (moderator) I can edit comments for compliance with correctness and censorship.

### №15

As an administrator, I can block users on the site to meet the interests of site / user when actions are contrary to the policy site.

### №16

As the creator of the service I provide feedback from users to improve service.

### №17

As an advertiser, I can advertise associated with binding to the sites to attract customers.